---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Multi-State Mobile Automotive Recall Services for Dealerships & Fleets</h1>
			<form
  action="https://www.nhtsa.gov/recalls"
  method="get"
  target="_blank"
  class="vin-form"
>
  <input
    type="text"
    name="vin"
    placeholder="Enter VIN (17 characters)"
    maxlength="17"
    required
  />
  <button type="submit">Check VIN for Recalls</button>
</form>

<a
  href="/schedule"
  style="
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:1.5rem;
    padding:0.9rem 1.6rem;
    background:#0f172a;
    color:white;
    font-weight:600;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:6px;
  "
>
  Schedule Free Recall Service
</a>

<p>
				Platinum Recall Team provides manufacturer-compliant recall repairs at your location — at no cost to the customer — across multiple U.S. states.
We’re a mobile recall service built to make OEM recalls effortless—for customers and partners alike. Our certified technicians come directly to the vehicle’s location and complete manufacturer-approved recall repairs on-site, at zero cost to the customer. No dealership visits, no downtime, no friction.

For fleets, dealers, and organizations, we increase recall completion rates, reduce liability, and protect brand trust—without adding operational burden. We handle the scheduling, logistics, and paperwork; you get safer vehicles, happier customers, and measurable results.

Simply put: we remove every barrier between an open recall and a completed repair.
			</p>
			<p>How It Works
			</p>
			<p>Schedule your recall service online, and our certified mobile technicians will come to your dealership or fleet location. Recalls are completed in compliance with manufacturer requirements at no cost to the customer.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Edit this page in <code>src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
				<li>Edit the site header items in <code>src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
				<li>Add your name to the footer in <code>src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
				<li>Check out the included blog posts in <code>src/content/blog/</code></li>
				<li>Customize the blog post page layout in <code>src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to <a href="https://docs.astro.build/"
					>read the docs
				</a> or <a href="https://astro.build/chat">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
			</p>
			<p>
				Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a
					href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template"
					>astro-blog-template
				</a> by <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
